story: Karim Eldomyati shared Be Koty's post to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Be Koty
description:
Now is the best time to achieve your Dream of Building your Own Business ( becoming an Internet Entrepreneur ) because we offer a great Business Opportunity for you, we are searching for the best Business Partners! Will you be one of us?

Our Vision is to help the world achieve more of they want.

If you believe in our vision and you feel passionate because you have something which you can do that will add value to people and to our project and you are ready to be a part of it, please contact Mr. Karim Eldomyati ( the Founder of Be Koty ) and send him your CV including your Business Dreams.
